Klopp: &ldquo;We have to strengthen the squad. Finding players that will improve the squad 200 per cent will be difficult but we have do some things to make the squad bigger.&rdquo;<br />
<br />
Klopp: &ldquo;We want a couple of players, but are only looking for good ones. The players we bring in we will all together be 100 per cent convinced about. It&rsquo;s been like this since I&rsquo;ve been here and will always be like that.&rdquo;
